<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Mid-year Break Stay</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="55cc3eb3-4a04-4572-93e5-da4d8a8cd305" >

    <p>The University and residences close for the mid-year break.&nbsp; Student are not permitted to stay in residence during the mid-year break, unless they apply and are approved to stay in&nbsp; the <a href="/content/ryerson/housing/future-students/residence-buildings.html">International Living and Learning Centre (ILC)</a>.&nbsp; The last day to stay in residence is Saturday December 19, 2020 until 12 pm (noon). Students can return to residence after the mid-year break at 12 pm (noon) on Sunday January 10, 2021.</p> 
<p>During the mid-year break, The ILC remains open with limited campus and residence services available.&nbsp; If you would like to stay on campus during this period, you will need to indicate this on your residence application so you can be assigned to the ILC.&nbsp; You will also need to complete a supplementary application in the fall term and be approved by Housing &amp; Residence Life in order to stay over the mid-year break. There will be an extra cost for your stay during the mid-year break period.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#55cc3eb3-4a04-4572-93e5-da4d8a8cd305");});</script></div>

				

				
