    <ul> 
 <li><strong>ILC Residence Services Desk</strong> - The desk will be staffed 24 hours/day throughout the mid-year break period.</li> 
 <li><strong>Limited Residence Life Support</strong> - There will be at least one Residence Advisor available each day/night of the mid-year break.</li> 
 <li><strong>Limited Maintenance/Cleaning Services</strong> - Maintenance and cleaning will be operating on a reduced schedule during the mid-year break, so the frequency of scheduled cleanings will be reduced and a longer wait time can be expected for work order requests.</li> 
