 <li><strong>Ryerson Eats</strong> - The residence cafeterias and all other food outlets on campus will be unavailable beginning on December (TBA on exact date), 2020 at 12 pm (noon). The residence cafeterias will open on Sunday January (TBA on exact date), 2021.</li> 
