                            If I indicated that I want to stay over the break in the residence application and change my mind, do I have to stay and/or pay for the stay?
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1599072444778-if-i-indicated-that-i-want-to-stay-over-the-break-in-the-residence-application-and-change-my-mind--do-i-have-to-stay-and-or-pay-for-the-stay-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1599072444778-if-i-indicated-that-i-want-to-stay-over-the-break-in-the-residence-application-and-change-my-mind--do-i-have-to-stay-and-or-pay-for-the-stay-">
