    <p><strong><span>No.</span></strong> You have the opportunity to cancel your interest in staying over the mid-year break until early December. &nbsp;Cancelling your interest to stay over the mid-year break removes your ability to stay over the break as well as your responsibility to pay for the mid-year break stay. &nbsp;Cancellations must be submitted in writing to <a href="mailto:housing@ryerson.ca">housing@ryerson.ca</a>.</p> 
<p>Cancellations after the early December deadline may be subject to a cancellation fee. &nbsp;</p> 
<p>Cancellations will not be accepted after Friday December 11, 2020 at 12 pm (noon). Residents trying to cancel at or beyond this time will remain responsible for the full mid-year break stay fee.</p>
    





</div>
